Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:43.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\3c&H000000&\blur4\3a85}连接因果的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:45.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\3c&H000000&\blur4\3a85}拨动那紧绷的丝线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:47.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\3c&H000000&\blur4\3a85}并唱响
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:51.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\3c&H000000&\blur4\3a85}那无法妥协的希望之歌
